Re: A Plague of Rats in Paris

32 min

Available until 16/06/2025

24/05/2023

  • Investigation and reports
  • Documentaries and Reportage

There are an estimated 6 million rats in Paris, more than twice the human population. Since the covid lockdowns, they are becoming ever bolder and have started to invade the streets of the city. How can the city manage the rodent problem?
